    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚维持利率不变以应对价格压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-maintains-hold-on-rates-as-it-weighs-price-pressures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚央行维持借贷成本不变，这一意外举措表明政策制定者在权衡持续的价格压力时采取了谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-maintains-hold-on-rates-as-it-weighs-price-pressures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 11:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典将为电池研究提供新支持，解雇工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/sweden-to-offer-new-support-for-battery-research-sacked-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典政府承诺将为该国刚刚起步的电池行业提供新的研究资金，并努力保留 Northvolt AB 裁员工人的技能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/sweden-to-offer-new-support-for-battery-research-sacked-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 10:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最高法院下令清算破产的捷特航空公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/india-s-top-court-orders-liquidation-of-bankrupt-jet-airways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院周四作出裁决，印度曾为第二大航空公司的捷特航空将进行清算，结束了这家破产航空公司长达五年的动荡破产清算历程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/india-s-top-court-orders-liquidation-of-bankrupt-jet-airways</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 10:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦央行将放松货币管制，允许津巴布韦元自由浮动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-to-ease-currency-reins-and-allow-free-float-of-zig</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦央行副行长表示，津巴布韦希望其以黄金为基础的货币能够在外汇市场上自由浮动，但他拒绝透露具体时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/-usd-zwg-zimbabwe-to-ease-currency-reins-and-allow-free-float-of-zig</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 10:28:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
